The contract must describe one coherent story arc with a gentle goal, a small non-scary obstacle, a kind resolution, and a cozy ending. The obstacle must stand directly between Glimsi and the goal — a feeling inside Glimsi (shy, unsure, worried about a first try) or one small concrete hitch — never an unrelated event. In the resolution, Glimsi personally takes the brave or kind step that overcomes exactly that obstacle — the supporting characters help and encourage, but Glimsi does it. The ending image must show the goal achieved. Use Glimsi as the hero. Choose exactly two supporting character names from: Mia, Ella, Rosa, Ruby, Daisy, Lucy, Lily, Anna, Zoe, Emma, Ben, Sam, Leo, Jack, Max, Tom, Noah, Finn.

